{"tid":1757450,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店系列 尖沙咀 博多拉麵別天神","createTime":"2019-11-26T13:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T17:26:43.000Z","uid":166062,"like":38,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b92b407c1d5e5e0f5581fc4a3506965cefc7dcc7","tid":1757450,"uid":166062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xp0gxax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXp0gxax.jpg&h=47ed72e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n105$套餐 拉麵加沙律/餃子<br />\n就咁拉麵75$ 沙律/餃子 35$ 都係平5蚊姐<br />\n我食左加沙律同再加10$麵底 一共115$<br />\n成年男性都夠飽 比唔上一籣 但絕對唔難食<br />\n有一點要留意 唔知其他分店係咪咁 <br />\n尖沙咀呢間只可以自助落單同比錢<br />\n姐係冇得比現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c2042931d38ba5aeb92e59bba7686c3456b498","tid":1757450,"uid":2419,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:57:33.000Z","msg":"個麵底難食 希望改善下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他ok 沙律好食"},{"pid":"935a9c60a5827b7eb7908844ff9eaa2419db0df0","tid":1757450,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":64,"score":-62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"味千拉麵屌打"},{"pid":"e2ae6973096b07a128f509561e5e14fb641821b7","tid":1757450,"uid":166062,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"935a9c60a5827b7eb7908844ff9eaa2419db0df0","tid":1757450,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":64,"score":-62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"味千拉麵屌打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"黃店屌打你啦 別天神真係食得落口既"},{"pid":"b5d78baa1705dfd9645d686fb5775ed9e6174c79","tid":1757450,"uid":11028,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:05:55.000Z","msg":"雖則係黃店<br />\n但平心而論<br />\n真係唔覺得好食<br />\n<br />\n但都會繼續幫襯"},{"pid":"0589109a70559a393c4547839a479fa795ab5ad9","tid":1757450,"uid":14366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"沙律好食<br />\n但係個面就唔係特別好..